{"tid":2084621,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"總加速師又一腳油門：將地方領導預備役部隊的權力收歸中央。","createTime":"2020-06-29T10:55:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T11:05:15.000Z","uid":58841,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c2dd9386ea3359a2932e40fd30e3893558ccb121","tid":2084621,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T10:55:41.000Z","msg":"近日，中共中央印發了《關於調整預備役部隊領導體制的決定》（以下簡稱《決定》）。《決定》明確，自2020年7月1日零時起，預備役部隊全面納入軍隊領導指揮體系，由現行軍地雙重領導調整為黨中央、中央軍委集中統一領導。<br />\n<br />\n    《決定》指出，預備役部隊是人民解放軍的組成部分，為全面貫徹黨的十九大和十九屆二中、三中、四中全會精神，堅持和完善黨對人民軍隊的絕對領導制度，確保實現黨在新時代的強軍目標，把人民軍隊全面建成世界一流軍隊，按照軍是軍、警是警、民是民的原則，對預備役部隊領導體制進行調整。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：人大審議相關條例，以取消待遇等手段做威脅，加強對退伍兵的管控；近期中印、南海、台海等地局勢較為緊張；<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/20935\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpincong.rocks%2Farticle%2F20935&d=Q4XCoHks6IcJcnuFSE4RTZLurRSHZiEGX9rhKonVocs%3D&h=90ae245a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://pincong.rocks/article/20935</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中央集權制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇黎三萬隻狗狗為国捐軀日子不遠了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a51a53aca1f64bb6a41a0ff5dbaa71950a39728","tid":2084621,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T10:58:12.000Z","msg":"送香港個三萬精兵上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cee14e5c6a6a822fae9c13e20bfdef2d6974287e","tid":2084621,"uid":78470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T10:58:52.000Z","msg":"送去印度幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62ad3caa560bbc58afe46ed27cb92a8d8b24f50c","tid":2084621,"uid":57671,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T10:59:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pWsavmb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpWsavmb.jpg&h=cd1318a2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na